{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "e08ddea0-3511-44a8-9f99-6c5c1d988af4", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e08ddea0-3511-44a8-9f99-6c5c1d988af4@6.pkg/1772602471358/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602471929", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e08ddea0-3511-44a8-9f99-6c5c1d988af4@6.pkg/1772602471358/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602471929"}, "identifier": "e08ddea0-3511-44a8-9f99-6c5c1d988af4", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>A．有误，“似的”应读作“shì de”；B．正确；C．有误，“脊”应读作“jǐ”；D．有误，“惩戒”应读作“chéng jiè”。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>1.下列词语中加点字的字音、字形完全正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "title": "1.下列词语中加点字的字音、字形完全正确的一项是（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e08ddea0-3511-44a8-9f99-6c5c1d988af4@6.pkg/item.json?v=1752031367812", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>失<span class=\"dot\">踪</span>（zōng） <span class=\"dot\">似</span>的（sì） &nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">颈</span>下（jǐng） &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">娱</span>乐（yú）</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>污<span class=\"dot\">涩</span>（sè） &nbsp;&nbsp;叮<span class=\"dot\">嘱</span>（zhǔ ）红<span class=\"dot\">绫</span>（líng） &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">怅</span>然（chàng）</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p><span class=\"dot\">怂</span>恿（sǒng） 屋<span class=\"dot\">脊</span>（jí） &nbsp;懒<span class=\"dot\">惰</span>（duò） &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">凝</span>望（níng）</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p><span class=\"dot\">蜷</span>伏（quán） 活<span class=\"dot\">泼</span>（pō） <span class=\"dot\">郁</span>闷（yù） &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"dot\">惩</span>戒（chěng）</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>1.下列词语中加点字的字音、字形完全正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5136342961", "5036342748", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5136342961", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "e08ddea0-3511-44a8-9f99-6c5c1d988af4", "global_title": {"zh-CN